Package: rstudio.quickwd
Title: RStudio Quick Working Directory — Add-Ins for Clipboard and Active File
Version: 2.2.1
Authors@R: person("HTang", email = "tang.heng@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Two RStudio add-ins (Windows, macOS, Linux): set working directory
    and the Files pane from a clipboard path, or from the on-disk path of the
    active editor tab (parent folder). Also exports 'quick_working_directory()'
    for a clipboard-first fallback when called from code. Uses 'clipr' and
    'rstudioapi'; on Linux you may need xclip, xsel, or wl-clipboard.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    clipr (>= 0.4),
    rstudioapi (>= 0.13)
